## HYLONO CONTEXT (always active)

- **Company**: European medtech, democratizing non-invasive regeneration technology
- **Modalities**: Oxygen (mHBOT), Hydrogen, Light (RLT/NIR), Signal (PEMF, VNS)
- **Tagline**: "where mind connects with matter"
- **Business model**: Protocol-as-product. Rental-first (primary), purchase (secondary), B2B/professional
- **USP**: Safety + Protocol + Access + Service + Integration
- **Markets**: EU-first. Priority locales: en, de, pl, nl
- **Stack**: React + TypeScript (strict) + Vite + Tailwind CSS + Prisma + PostgreSQL
- **Regulatory**: EU MDR aware, GDPR mandatory, health-adjacent content requires disclaimers
